Citibank is a major International Banks Bank. There is no Citibank branch location in the city of Davis, however Citibank users can use the Citibank ATMs ATM at 7Eleven and any MoneyPass branded ATM such as US Bank or Yolo Federal Credit Union without a fee.

Citibank announced on September 29, 2008 that it was going to buy the banking operations of Wachovia. However, Wells Fargo offered a larger amount of money to buy all of Wachovia. After talks, Citibank decided to give up and let Wells Fargo take over Wachovia.

